{"h5adf321egd11dg45f1gb70eg64f4c59b2105": ["Ugh. Later. Ground's spinning.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "fdbd10e9-dbc6-e5a2-baef-928fe711951f"], "h90a64d8eg6641g4178g84bcg7384306f0ab4": ["You sure know how to keep a party interesting.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "2f8118c9-9c6a-6a67-6565-4cef5ecb4f6e"], "hfabc4829gbc5fg4bc8gaf7bg1fc666379218": ["Makes me wonder if you treat all your lovers that harshly.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "c203fe6f-654d-23fc-4e98-72e66263e8d4"], "hdf6e81eeg6168g4109gb532g5def4f6c3638": ["At least you've spared them the hangover tomorrow.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "dbdbb985-72e6-493b-e6e5-62dae10a49a6"], "h9aa4e111g5608g4c4dg9907g644c96e09c74": ["Shouldn't you be in someone else's bedroll by now?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "1b7cf718-21a6-e609-d74b-d9c47840646b"], "h45059133gaf75g4b0dgbdc6g84cde2566bf5": ["The fire's nice. I'll stay here a while.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "8e64c2d3-fc75-a08c-aa2a-24eee162e868"], "hf8da6f7eg067cg4a3cgbb74gdd873ef350e6": ["Entertain yourself elsewhere.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "ca84fd57-d2f8-98a2-a435-e89e2eb2fff6"], "heb984b50g5ac2g4fbfg8bf2g50fb04b0dc31": ["What a glorious celebration. Hip-deep in gore.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "f2d4eeae-0972-bab4-ee08-7c9fd8485d60"], "hc1992e2bgbc3bg4400gb496gc6622ab0c99b": ["And you're carousing with Astarion.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "910dfdc6-53b2-8e38-452e-5a73bd82c13e"], "he57cc24fg1721g4505g9896g77c36fc187b3": ["The corpses probably do something extra for him, don't they?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "8357f095-b9e8-4cfd-19cd-c83ae5136fdc"], "hf98ca598gac9fg4465ga67fg091f588edb3b": ["Not that I'm judging. I have this.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "43d9ce09-e0da-3553-3582-b307dd432b13"], "hdeb39826g3d19g4a86g94bdg9521e060c242": ["He does seem like the decadent type.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "1f03d0aa-4bac-f9fb-82f2-0c8d7cb75411"], "h27783584g0575g47a0ga86age42ec863d986": ["And you're carousing with Lae'zel.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "39c1d419-1fee-38e0-2b57-41515b869681"], "h7eed9ffbg7f71g4ccega632g8d4f4f9032f4": ["I'm surprised she hasn't dragged you off to rut already.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "050daa0f-f69e-cc52-a512-a84a316e747a"], "h575b0297ga06dg45b9gb5dag0891bcd3fe8b": ["And you're carousing with Minthara.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "c254d7ce-1bf8-9bb2-a396-bb4cc7eebc01"], "hbe81ab1bg8431g4176ga6adg7ad4f47c3fab": ["Careful that she doesn't take a piece of you as a souvenir.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "ebef77c3-4a07-ef5a-380e-4fee12b6e336"], "h04e27696ga7a5g4d59gb200gbb9ee46615ec": ["The goblins stole good wine. It goes straight to the head.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "2ec973ca-6ac2-4d0f-c6dd-c245e18f7d4c"], "hd8ee0ba7g292dg49c2g904fgfa044e55a7c9": ["You're tearing through that bottle. Is something wrong?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "f396b6e5-a851-7010-8036-6993403c37fd"], "h736e6748gd2aag4c86gb015gb041d6cb2588": ["What's wrong with enjoying a gift from our guests?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "ffea0390-2eb3-52e6-058b-6a99aabbe011"], "h13e9a5e3g3442g4ba1g9199g9f16f39ade23": ["Maybe if I down enough of this swill, it'll pickle the worm in my skull.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "093e4538-0de1-ffc8-b369-c25f91a76ca9"], "h5f921385g903cg4d59ga268g01f0ec53d20a": ["Aren't you excited? We won.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "3c739fd2-799a-ce78-2baa-5d60f2c756a2"], "heb63251eg665bg4637gb68fg82cdd827707a": ["We set a pack of refugees on fire. A child could have done it.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "0c884e47-8268-b66d-d79a-67b4d311740a"], "h9f239a4bg8b44g4fdag9f1eg4e543b30c88c": ["Not exactly an ambush for the ages.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "ffb8779d-7f4a-9b32-536c-9bc5af3616a6"], "hb5a5291cgfd11g4846gbb1ag5fc3bc833217": ["Would you like a better distraction?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "aa33acbf-ac9e-96de-46be-f7a31bfe29b1"], "h17f18627ge8d5g46a4g882cg20115e77647b": ["Maybe... but I know better than to share my bed drunk.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "4044b285-5e47-6d84-4a14-a725e9e37cdf"], "hbd5424afgd3dfg4cd2g9c33g2876389b5d9e": ["Unless you meant to raise my spirits by other means?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "26c4fd65-9140-cc18-3895-c76065e8c245"], "hc6dfd5d8gd9aeg475dgaa35gdc814e91b255": ["We could sit by the fire?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "615ec519-944b-c246-09fb-9f4ccbeb6e16"], "hee0652f9g3859g41b9ga87cg3a79f3ffb8d1": ["Ah, sitting. Such an engaging activity.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "ecde2968-ddd9-4ee0-cc28-2731d8d27fde"], "ha6476d79gde8eg4757g85abg5e6dc2d4eeaa": ["But that... doesn't sound half bad.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "367ab6e6-005a-17e2-b64e-9a072255631a"], "h8070bf78g27d6g473dgb98eg50cac46eef72": ["Certainly not. I find your misery amusing.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "c87045d0-b357-e0a3-8e22-fe685f28fc16"], "h00563d65ge3c3g4cf7ga6d2gd43cbd5bf751": ["Well, I don't find you entertaining in the least.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "8d29e6ec-2474-0229-fbbd-7e53db45b7bf"], "hdce4b03bg3cb7g40a7gad8aga68d8d6b7ba8": ["In fact, I prefer the wine to your blind stabs at mockery. Get away from me.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "007c7d3f-3e75-e95c-c12f-12610e266aa8"], "h3d282481g2d40g4dffgb2c9gc8782ebf902d": ["You could share what's on your mind - if you want.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "c48948e6-f74f-030e-d755-6cd2ec5abf93"], "hc0672150gd0cdg46d9g88e8g440513a9258a": ["I prefer to keep a few things secret. It's old habit.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "8821c2f4-7d8b-6814-76d3-9756aa33807a"], "h10711463g3a4fg47ddgb1e2g8958d0f621b5": ["Thank you. The offer's kind, but it's not a kindness I can afford.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "d41ce278-081b-dbb8-91ed-56766c5974db"], "h7cf21433g4017g4e8bg8d8agec3f60b2ecbb": ["I'm not sure what to say. I've never done any of this... comforting.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "de6d8787-5c9c-cda2-a488-bf6819530129"], "h275709b3ga1f6g4ddcga3e4g96059f8cd795": ["It's awkward for me too, you know.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "bb9c1b73-362e-aa8b-25eb-c69e74c208d8"], "h1d1f9c0bg5723g434fgad2bg3bb50b3f68d8": ["But I appreciate the thought.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "167b8ae6-0b69-2599-ca7c-c49f89037a49"], "h881f4186g78d3g4d28gab02g1924294ba441": ["How about a warsong? Something to celebrate your triumph.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "fa58f87c-6416-58da-eb96-d5cae9c6d66d"], "h132ce922g00b3g466fgb40cg8d7baa840acb": ["No more war tonight, I think.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "7b7296c0-4eed-5221-955f-8f7f9912ead2"], "he91dc48cg7379g41f9gbeccg043e8addcc24": ["I'd prefer the quiet, if it's all the same to you.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "c2d05975-5a07-e29a-2018-52c857ee6b73"], "hcccc64a2gdb34g4ef5g9483g577be31986e9": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "7aa55499-8cdd-fe88-b416-f68b22e797b6"], "h32a24fe2gf629g40cdg92b2g03b33ce9338e": ["Get a girl's hopes up, why don't you? I need another bottle.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "0b4c5398-b853-34f2-8ffe-930049f384ca"], "h79a88c7dg130dg47d2ga0f5g6b095a1ed96f": ["Not interested in a vampire's leftovers, I'm afraid.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "fb3130b7-3ac0-8fed-ab99-3100aa4ddf61"], "hf324fdebg9d9dg421cga623gc115fcb8b44a": ["Not interested in Astarion's leftovers, I'm afraid.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "529467fd-5bff-f1b1-8115-958539001727"], "h45c5430eg131eg49d6gbbd9gec6fb7a641f9": ["Not interested in a gith's leftovers, I'm afraid.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "b3263a96-91e5-3bae-1744-b6faaca46d69"], "h68eb4d7dgca08g493ag8e5fge40114272b5c": ["Not interested in Minthara's leftovers, I'm afraid.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "bc4ff938-9e7b-f42a-9cd8-d4b4fcefec3d"], "h98c5bcb9gce4fg467cgb711g5443cff5d652": ["Pull yourself together. Your behaviour is unbecoming.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "da291dab-103e-76ec-adf3-a7f25bfb2e77"], "h904c3383gc8b0g4eb9g8e71g47d7fea69255": ["You're the one becoming! Disgusting...", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "a50a2a15-828f-91df-9915-2162c6fec8ac"], "h2a25c226g3bccg4874g93dcgd5a3c4f47d39": ["... it's all disgusting.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "80f1eff6-4795-d3d1-8145-51cc0d2b2558"], "h6953aefagec68g4e15g9517g06e9ba59ebb9": ["You look guilty. Tormented.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "8df11def-3562-bc2a-1609-16090f406eaf"], "ha30a5e0ag4014g4299g83c1g696abdfd999d": ["Guilty? Ridiculous. What's there to be guilty for?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "daf963c0-2158-83b5-2070-7a0915c23c2a"], "h03801205g886fg481bgbc0cg31d56a6ee43b": ["I serve the Lady of Loss. We stripped those tieflings of hope itself.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "06ca323f-550c-c332-c9f9-42de8ad6a184"], "hc850c83bgf034g4053gbb7ag7cda98f463b0": ["Just... let me enjoy a drink in peace.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "b79824c5-8f8b-41cc-ef1c-feadff8151a6"], "h2c6f592eg218fg4bb3g889fg2acbb03ec175": ["My goddess smiles on such bloodshed.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "72159c6e-5aa3-f68e-fb2d-d308674aa806"], "h57681750g2885g4d1bg8adfg38920fbe45bc": ["<i>Will your magic to pierce Shadowheart's thoughts.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "e37e0d5e-2389-58d9-a222-200edd016165"], "h608c9476gfa1dg41e2g8b2eg702ea7aa12ca": ["<i>Why did killing those tieflings make me feel sick?</i>", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "407b6566-5cc6-ae47-2349-9a4413fb47e9"], "h27a71b9ag60dcg4c6egaeddg0257827142d6": ["<i>I've killed in her name before. Why now? Why isn't the wine helping?</i>", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "9f12eefc-5af9-a6c3-9060-b7f23faf5d61"], "h1fb1de2ag00dcg4b38gbc40g457fca02e14b": ["<i>Push into her thoughts.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "84654695-381a-ed9f-d470-ed06e50ab4f2"], "h0c7e4814g4775g414egbc4cg3485f000e0c2": ["*Shadowheart's mind is drenched in drink and confusion. She's killed before - enjoyed it, even.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "8411b0b3-0604-bf80-19e8-635bf8b73fc6"], "h08ff51d8gbbaag4e19g9998ga76c1ab2535b": ["*But now an ill, twisting feeling lingers in her gut. One that has nothing to do with the wine.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "3412c7d8-c668-de8e-bc44-a7cf568f043b"], "h75ba3950g4f71g4f43gb315gb09678f6cd98": ["*Your head swims, nausea burning in your gut.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "cf42b123-595a-2d9e-8e61-191f90c632c0"], "h64923289gf6d0g4d09gab7bgc6df63148d72": ["You just... you! Get away from me. Now.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "80dceebd-7c4c-2935-d215-138ed878f480"], "h29e47ffag6e02g4a05g98a2gd3a4bf97c972": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "a87e46d6-e521-08d8-ed27-f203cb9ddcdb"]}